msgid ""
"Spring Framework instruments various parts of its own codebase to publish "
"observations if an `ObservationRegistry` is configured.  You can learn more "
"about {spring-boot-docs-ref}/actuator/observability.html[configuring the "
"observability infrastructure in Spring Boot]."
