#. type: Plain text
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/integration/observability.adoc:161
msgid ""
"You will need to configure the `ObservationRegistry` on the `JmsTemplate` to "
"enable observations:"
